c: 61
v: 6
t: "And (remember) when, Isa (Jesus), the son of Maryam (Mary), said: \"O Children of Israel! I am a messenger of Allah (sent) to you, reaffirming Torah (the Torah, that came) before me, and giving the good news of a Messenger (reference to the Prophet Muhammad) to come after me, whose name shall be Ahmad.\" But when he (the Prophet) came to them with clear proofs, they said, \"This is clearly magic (aimed at deception)"